Advantages:
terraform code is simple to understand
can be used with multiple vendoes (aws,azure,ibm,gcs).but code will change to cloud to cloud
config can be split into multiple files
can form dry-run easily .(it will check code easily)
Importing of manual created resources.
Reusable code
DisAdvantages:
Its 3rd party tool,new services might not available
bugs (latest version having many bugs)
lack of support



